\id JAS - Kalam NT [kmh] -Papua New Guinea 1992 (DBL 2014) 
\h Jemis 
\toc1 Minj Jemis Tikak 
\toc2 Jemis 
\toc3 Jem 
\mt1 JEMIS  
\mt2 Minj Jemis Tikak  
\imt1 Minim Nind Niŋep  
\ip Baybol buk day kisen ak tikyak ñin ak, Jemis omiŋal nokom mindyiŋgipay. Pen minj kun biy biynimb kuŋaynep Jiysis numam kisen Jemis tikip rek ayip aŋgiy niŋbay. Nuk Jiwda biynimb miñmon okok maŋgiysek, Gor nup gosimb niŋbun apay gok, minim nep ma aŋgiy, tap siy tap timey ak kirgiy, Gor aŋgip rek giyiŋg, nup gosimb nokom niŋiy, Jiysis Krays nup chiŋgrep giy gem amnimuŋ aŋgiy tikak.  
\iot Minim Ar Keykey Mindip Rek:  
\io1 Minim nind aŋgak ak mindip, chapta 1:1.  
\io1 Miker gunap apek, Gor nup ma kirgiy, nup nep gosimb niŋyiŋg, mindenimimb aŋgak minim ak mindip, chapta 1:2-8.  
\io1 Biynimb tap ma mindip gok sek, biynimb tap kuŋay mindip gok sek minim ak mindip, chapta 1:9-11.  
\io1 Biynimb miker apek, Gor nup ma kirpay minim ak mindip, chapta 1:12-18.  
\io1 Minim aŋgniŋgiy rek niŋiy, ginimimb aŋgak minim ak mindip, chapta 1:19-27.  
\io1 Biynimb teptep gok sek, biynimb tam okok mindpay gok sek kuyip, miñ ar nokom kun ak nep ginimimb aŋgak minim ak mindip, chapta 2:1-13.  
\io1 Biynimb Jiysis nup gosimb niŋbun apay gok, minim nep ma aŋgiy, tap siy tap timey gipay ak kirgiy, Gor aŋgip rek giniŋgiy aŋgak minim ak mindip, chapta 2:14-26.  
\io1 Biynimb Krays ker mindpim gok, joŋimb nimb ak kond mindrep ginimimb aŋgak minim ak mindip, chapta 3:1-18.  
\io1 Biynimb Krays ker mindpun gok, biynimb yikop gok gipay miñ ar ak, ma ginjun aŋgak minim ak mindip, chapta 4:1–5:6.  
\io1 Gor nup gosimb nokom niŋiy, Jiysis andkind winiŋgamb ak gos sek kond mindyiŋg, biynimb tap gip gok kuyip, Gor nup aŋgniŋnimimb aŋgak minim ak mindip, chapta5:7-20.  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 Yand Jemis, Gor apiymiŋay kuyip woŋg giñimbiyn. Nimbip Jiwda biynimb jiw am miñmon key okok mindiy, Gor nup gosimb niŋbim gok, “Nimb mindpim?” aspiyn.   
\s1 Miker Apek, Gos Kuŋay Ma Niŋnimimb  
\p
\v 2 Mam ay sikop. Miker apek, gos kuŋay ma niŋnimimb; tep gakniŋ nep mindenimimb.  
\v 3 Kosyam mindeniŋgambun rek, Gor nup chiŋgrep giy mey, kisen miker yerip apek, ma pirikniŋgambun.  
\v 4 Nup chiŋgiy nep mindiy mey, mindrep giy ma apyap pikniŋgambun.  
\v 5 Pen nimb gunap, yerer gon tep giniŋgamb aŋgiy, Gor bi chinup direp yimb gip anup aŋgniŋem, nimbip gos tep yipund giy ak ñiniŋgamb. Nup aŋgniŋey, yip yenen aŋgniŋbim aŋgiy, ma kirgip.  
\v 6 Kun ak nup aŋgniŋniŋg, gos nokom niŋiy aŋgniŋnimimb. Pen chinup niŋniŋgamb akaŋ, ma niŋniŋgamb aŋgiy, gos omiŋal niŋiy aŋgniŋeniŋgambim; yiŋgen apiy, ñiŋg solwara paŋgiy dand doŋ wiy gip rek ak giniŋgambim.  
\v 7-8 Biynimb kun gok rek, gos niŋrep giy ma gey amimb: gosow gosow niŋyiŋg gey amimb ak mey, Gor nup aŋgniŋbay ak, tap bap kuyip ginimuŋ rek ma ayip.   
\p
\v 9 Mam ay simbgeprek gok, Gor kuyip direp gek mindrep giniŋgambay ñin ak, miñmiñ giniŋgiy;  
\v 10 pen mam ay tap kuŋay mindip gok, tap kiyk apyownimuŋ ñin ak, miñmiñ giniŋgiy. Yenen: biynimb tap kuŋay mindeniŋgamb gok, mon sum rek luŋg yowniŋgambay.  
\v 11 Pumb ak lim giy, mon sum teprep kun ak niŋek, milip giy luŋg yowip. Biynimb tap kuŋay mindeniŋgamb gok, woŋg kiyk gi dand amniyakniŋ, kuyip kun ak rek giniŋgamb.  
\v 12 Pen biynimb miker apek, Gor nup ma kirgiy, chiŋgrep giy nep mindeniŋgambay gok, miñmiñ giniŋgiy. Biynimb nup wasemb aypay gok kuyip aŋgak rek, arband perper mindep ak ayñiniŋgamb.   
\p
\v 13-14 Biynimb timey gun aŋgiy gos ak apek, Gor gos ñek kun giy niŋbun aŋgiy, ma aŋgniŋgiy. Gor tap siy tap timey ma yimb gip rek, biynimb gunap kuyip, gos kun ak rek ma ñiniŋgamb. Pen gos kiyk key niŋbay ar ak, kuyip lipiŋg dand amek, tap siy tap timey gipay.  
\v 15 Gos niŋbun kun ak, tap yiŋ rek yimon, jakiy kindiy am wosgip rek ak; tap siy tap timey gipun. Tap timey gipun kun ak, pisnep mind wosgek, kumiy kuyiŋg yowniŋgambun.   
\p
\v 16 Pen mam ay tep yand gok. “Minim yesek bap aŋgeniŋgiy,” ma niŋnimimb.  
\v 17 Tap tep yipund giy yerip yerip dipun gok, key okok nimb apek ma dipun: Bapiy yomb melik tep gayak ak nep, chinup ñimb. Nuk miñ ar bap gi dand amiy, tap kawnan rek tuŋgandikiy, miñ ar bap key ma giniŋgamb.  
\v 18 Gos nuk key niŋiy gek, minim yipul yimb nup ak niŋiy donuk mey; biynimb tep nuk, tap marip nind maŋgiy miñmiñ giyiŋg pipaŋgipay rek ak mindpun.   
\s1 Niŋrep Giy Mindrep Ginimimb  
\p
\v 19 Mam ay tep yand gok niŋim! Nimbip minim aŋgñiyakniŋ, kasek niŋnimimb. Pen biynimb aŋg gun aŋgiy, kasek miluk ma niŋnimimb.  
\v 20 Biynimb miluk niŋon, kuyip gos tep ñek, Gor biynimb suŋ-tep nuk mindon aŋgiy, ma niŋniŋgambay.  
\v 21 Kun ak, gos timey niŋiy, timey gipim rek, yenen kun gipun aŋgiy kirgiy, Gor gos tep ñimb ar ak giy mey, kim amemb rek ayniŋgamb.   
\p
\v 22 Gor minim ak timund ak nep pik niŋiy, niŋbun aŋgiy ma aŋgnimimb. Ak tom giniŋgambim. Aŋgip rek giy mey; niŋbun aŋgnimimb.  
\v 23 Pen biynimb minim nup niŋiy, aŋgip rek ma gipay gok, galas ak niŋiy, jomluk niŋbun rek ak gipay.  
\v 24 Galas ay niŋiy, jomluk kiyk yerip rek mindip aŋgiy niŋrep gipay ak pen; kiriŋg amiy, sakiy giy; yergiy rek mindip aŋgiy, ma niŋbay.  
\v 25 Pen low tep yimb biynimb piksak dip ak sakiy ma giy, niŋyiŋg nep gey amniŋgamb biynimb gok, Gor kuyip kond mindek, yerer giniŋgambay ak amrep giniŋgamb.   
\p
\v 26 Pen biynimb, lotiw niŋind yimb giy mindrep gipun apay gok, joŋimb kiyk ak niŋrep giy ma apay; yesek aŋgyiŋg, key niŋyiŋg gi mindpay. Kiyk lotiw minim niŋbay ak, yikop yimb niŋbay.  
\v 27 Lotiw miñ ar Bapiy Gor niŋek tep gip ak mey; ñapan amoñiluk gok sek, biyn kaŋil simbgeprek gok sek kuyip, direp ginimimb. Pen biynimb yikop gok yip yiŋgoŋg giy, asiŋ kuyip kun ak ma wiliknimimb.   
\c 2  
\s1 Biynimb Gok Tep Biynimb Gok Timey Ma Aŋgep  
\p
\v 1 Mam ay sikop. Nimb Biyomb tep Jiysis Krays nup gosimb niŋbim rek, gos yesek okok niŋiy, biynimb bilok keykey ma aynimimb.  
\v 2-3 Pen lotiw giniŋg ap nan-giyiŋg, biynimb tap kuŋay mindakniŋ, chech tep tep ay, riyŋ teprep ñin maŋgiy kiyk ay apey niŋiy, kuyip aŋgem am pom ar teprep gok bisgey; biynimb simbgeprek gok apey niŋiy, aŋgem lum ar bisginiŋgambay akaŋ, jakiy nep mindeniŋgambay ak,  
\v 4 yipund ma giniŋgamb. Nimb key gos timey niŋiy, kun giy bilok ayniŋgambim.   
\p
\v 5 Pen mam ay tep yand gok niŋim! Gor biynimb simbgeprek kun gok kuyip, kun ak rek ma gip. Nuk kuyip gos tep ñek, biynimb gin yimb nuk gok mindiy, nuk yip biynimb kond mindeniŋgambay.  
\v 6-7 Biynimb kun gok rek, Gor nup dipay ak pen, nimb kuyip yenen aŋgem, lum ar ak nambiŋ gakniŋ bispay? Pen biynimb tap kuŋay mindip gok nep, Biyomb tep nimbip dip ak nup aŋgjiwiy, nimbip aŋg sikoy giy, dam kor gipay.   
\p
\v 8 Pen Baybol buk ak tikiy aŋgyak, “Biynimb gok kuyip, nand key wasemb aypan rek, wasemb aynimin aŋgyak.” Gor aŋgak rek kindik giniŋgambim ak, tep yimb.  
\v 9 Pen chech tap gok aypay rek niŋiy bilok ayniŋgambim ak; Gor minim ak timbrikiy, minim yomb diniŋgambim.   
\p
\v 10 Yenen: Gor low nuk gok niŋdiy, nokom bap timbrikniŋgambun ak, Gor niŋek maŋgiysek timbrikpun rek ayniŋgamb.  
\v 11 Gor nuk nokom, biyn siy bi siy ma ginimimb aŋgiy, chip ma ñaŋgnimimb aŋgiy gak. Kun ak chip ma ñaŋgiy, pen biyn siy bi siy giniŋgambun ak, minim nup timbrikniŋgambun. Pen biyn siy bi siy ma giy, chip ñaŋgniŋgambun ak, kunep minim nup ak timbrikniŋgambun.   
\p
\v 12 Kun ak minim aŋgniŋg akaŋ, yerer giniŋg, gos bap niŋiy aŋgnimimb, “Gor low tep nuk biynimb gok kuyip, tuŋgasik kim dip ak niŋiy, chinup kor giniŋgamb ak mey; mindrep ginjun aŋgnimimb.”  
\v 13 Biynimb simb ma niŋbay gok kuyip kor giy, simb ma niŋniŋgamb; pen biynimb simb niŋniŋgambay gok kuyip, simb niŋniŋgamb.   
\s1 Minim Nep Ma Aŋgnimimb  
\p
\v 14 Mam ay tep yand gok niŋim! Biynimb mindrep ma gipay gunap, Gor nup gosimb niŋbun aŋgniŋgambay ak pen, yikop yimb kun aŋgniŋgambay. Minim nep aŋgiy, tap bap ma giniŋgambay ak, kuyip yergiy diniŋgamb.   
\p
\v 15-16 Mam ay chech ma mindiy, keñmaŋgiy ma mindiy giniŋgamb gok niŋiy, tap dam ñiyiŋg mer: yikop, amiy mindrep ginimimb aŋgniŋgambun ak, yesek yimb kun aŋgniŋgambun. Kuyip tap gunap ñiyiŋg rek, minim kun ak aŋgjun.  
\v 17 Pen Gor aŋgip ar ak giyiŋg rek, nup gosimb niŋbun aŋgjun!   
\p
\v 18 Nimb gunap aŋgniŋgambim, “Chin biynimb gunap, Krays nup gosimb niŋbun, gunap aŋgip aŋgip rek giy, mindrep gipun ak mey, minim ma mindip aŋgniŋgambim.” Pen minim aŋgniŋgambim kun ak, nimbip pen aŋgniŋgayn, “Biynimb gok Gor nup gosimb niŋbun aŋgiy pen, yergiy aŋgip rek ma gipay aŋgniŋgayn”. Yand Krays nup gosimb niŋiy mey, aŋgip rek gipiyn.  
\v 19 Nimb Gor nokom nep mindip aŋgiy, gosimb niŋbim ak tep gipim. Pen kichekiy malñiluk gok kunep, gosimb ar kun anep niŋiy, pirikiy jep dipay.  
\v 20 Nimb sakiy sek! Gor nup gosimb niŋbun apim ak pen, aŋgip rek ma giy, minim nep apim.   
\p
\v 21 Nimb niŋbim: basind Ebraham Gor nup gosimb nokom niŋak rek, ñinuk Aysek nup pik Gor nup simboŋgniŋg gek, nuk niŋiy, ak bi suŋrep yand aŋgak.  
\v 22 Kun ak Ebraham gosimb nep niŋek, nup bi suŋrep yand ma aŋgak, Gor nup gosimb niŋiy aŋgak rek gek mey, bi suŋrep yand aŋgak.  
\v 23 Ñin kun ak mey, Baybol buk aŋgiy tikyak rek, Ebraham Gor nup gosimb niŋek mey, Gor nup bi suŋrep yand aŋgak. Gak kun ak, Gor Ebraham nup, buŋgiy yand aŋgak.  
\v 24 Kun ak niŋim! Gosimb ak nep niŋiy, Gor yip jimñiy ma mindeniŋgambun; nup gosimb niŋiy aŋgip rek giy mey, nuk yip jimñiy mindeniŋgambun.   
\p
\v 25 Kun ak rek nep, biyn Reyap gak. Nuk kinjeŋram biyn mindyiŋgip ak pen; bi Yisrel omiŋal aperik, Reyap biynimb nuk gok, kuyipmiŋay pikayniŋg geyak, nuk niŋiy kasin gek mey, piyow mer niŋyak. Kisen kuyipmiŋay aŋgyokek, pirik kinjeŋ ar bap amiy, korip amnirik. Reyap gak rek niŋiy, Gor biyn suŋrep yand aŋgak.  
\v 26 Pen biynimb mumbwak nep mindiy, kawnan sek ma mindpay ak, kim mindeniŋgiy rek ma ayip. Kun ak rek, biynimb Gor nup gosimb niŋbun aŋgiy, pen aŋgip ar ak ma gipay.   
\c 3  
\s1 Joŋimb Chin Niŋrep Ginjun  
\p
\v 1 Mam ay Krays ker mindpim gok. Nimb kuŋaynep tiysa mindonjun aŋgiy, ma niŋnimimb. Chin tiysa gok, kor kilis rek niŋniŋgambun.  
\v 2 Chin maŋgiysek yipund ma gip ar gok keykey gipun. Pen biynimb joŋimb kiyk kond mindrep giy, minim yipund giniŋgamb ar ak nep aŋgniŋgambay gok, amemb wep kiyk gok, maŋgiysek niŋrep giniŋgiy rek ayniŋgamb.  
\v 3 Kanj hos gok yomb yimb ak pen; tap ayen sikoy par bap miñ ak sek tiwniŋgiy, di meŋg miŋgan ak ay, amniŋg gipay okok ken lip gey ambay.  
\v 4 Siyip yomb gok kunep, yiŋgen apiy dand yesek okok ambikop ak pen, bi kapten gok stiya sikoy ak diy, amniŋg gipay okok ken di yipund gey amimb.  
\v 5 Joŋimb chin ak sikoy ak pen, minim aŋgon kuŋaynep ayip. Pen saŋgiy yomb yimb namb ak, sikoy band bap sup ñey, yin dand amiy, maŋgiysek yinimuŋ rek mindip.  
\v 6 Mumbwak day chin ak, timey kun ak rek bap sek ma mindip; joŋimb ak nep mon maŋlaŋ rek mindiy, amemb wep chinup ak maŋgiysek gi timey gip. Pen mon maŋlaŋ kun ak, miñmon Hel ak nimb apiy, mey kun gip.   
\p
\v 7 Kimin yakir, siyŋ saraw, tap saŋgiy okok mindip gok sek, tap ñiŋg solwara okok mindip gok sek dand apiy mokey, gos niŋbay ak pen;  
\v 8 joŋimb chin ak aŋgon, gos niŋnimuŋ rek ma mindip. Timey yimb giy, biynimb pik aynimuŋ rek ayip.  
\v 9 Joŋimb chin ak, Gor Bapiy yomb anup tep aŋgyiŋg, biynimb nuk rek niŋiy gayak gok kuyip, aŋgjiwyiŋg gipun.  
\v 10 Joŋimb nokom kun ak nep, minim tep aŋgyiŋg, timey aŋgyiŋg gipun. Mam ay sikop. Yenen kun ginjun? Ak tep ma giniŋgamb.  
\v 11 Ñiŋg kilam nokom bap jiwiy, ñiŋg tep gunap, ñiŋg timey gunap ma wip.  
\v 12 Mon ak, miñ maŋgiy ma piyniŋgamb; miñ ak, mon maŋgiy ma piyniŋgamb. Pen ñiŋg timey ak, ñiŋg kim tep molep rek ma ayniŋgamb. Kun ak mam ay sikop. Joŋimb chin ak minim timey gok sek ma aŋgjun.   
\s1 Miluk Niŋiy Asik Keykey Ma Aynimimb  
\p
\v 13 Nimb gos niŋrep gipim? Niŋrep ginimimb ak, yimb nimb key ma dand aranimimb; gos tep niŋbim rek, Gor nup tep ginimuŋ ar ak ginimimb.  
\v 14 Pen gosimb namb nimb biyaŋ yiruk gek, miluk niŋiy, yimb nimb key ma dand aranimimb. Minim yesek gok aŋgiy, minim yipul yimb ak ma taw yiw ginimimb.  
\v 15 Biynimb gos tep niŋbun aŋgiy, timey kun ak rek gipay gok, Gor gos ñimb ar ak ma gipay; biynimb yikop niŋbay rek nep niŋiy, Seytan nup kisen gipay.  
\v 16 Pen miluk niŋyiŋg, asik keykey ay, timey ar ak gon amek, mindrep ma yimb giniŋgambun.   
\p
\v 17 Gor gos ñimb rek niŋiy mey, suŋ nep mindiy, tep ar ak giyiŋg, kapkap mindrep giyiŋg, biynimb simb niŋiy direp giyiŋg, minim andikiy andikiy ma aŋgniŋgambun. Gor nup tep giniŋgamb ar ak giy, biynimb tep gok mindiy, minim aŋg yiw yiw giyiŋg, minim okok nimb okok nimb ma aŋgniŋgambun.  
\v 18 Kapkap mindrep giniŋgambun kun ak, tap yiŋ yimbay rek yimoniŋgambun mey; jak yomb giy, maŋgiy teprep Gor niŋek, tep giniŋgamb gok piyniŋgamb.   
\c 4  
\s1 Gor Nup Chiŋgrep Gep  
\p
\v 1 Per miluk yapek penpen gipim ak, gos timey biynimb yikop gok niŋbay rek nep niŋiy, kun gipim.  
\v 2 Tap diniŋg niŋbim gok ma diy, kalrimey jiwiy, biynimb pikayun aŋgiy gipim. Tap tep gok ma dinimimb rek ayek, penpen aŋgiy, penpen gun aŋgiy niŋbim. Gor nup aŋgniŋiy dipkip ak pen, nup ma aŋgniŋbim.  
\v 3 Pen nup aŋgniŋbim ñin gok, gos tep niŋiy ma aŋgniŋbim; chinup key tep gaŋ aŋgiy aŋgniŋbim ak mey, apim rek ma gip.   
\p
\v 4 Pen biynimb Gor nup chiŋgrep ma gipim gok, yenen kun gipim? Biynimb gos kiyk tap mankumb biy ker nep amimb gok, Gor nup miluk niŋiy mey, tap kun gok nep gos niŋbay.  
\v 5 Ar kun ak Baybol buk tikiy aŋgyak, “Gos chin ar gunap key amek, nup tep ma giniŋgamb aŋgyak.” Pen minim kun ak niŋem yikop rek ayip?  
\v 6 Minim nuk ak chinup kond mindrep yimb giniŋgamb. Ar kun ak nep, Baybol buk ak tikiy aŋgyak:  
\q1 “Biynimb keynep mindiy, mindrep gipun apay gok, Gor kuyip minim yiñ rek aŋgip; pen biynimb yimb kiyk key ma dand aranimbay gok simb niŋiy, direp yimb gip aŋgyak.”   
\p
\v 7 Kun ak Gor nup pis ak mindiy, Seytan nup mer nep aŋgem mey, nimbip kiriŋg amniŋgamb.  
\v 8 Gor nup chiŋgrep gem, nimbip chiŋgrep giniŋgamb. Nimb biynimb tap siy tap timey gem ñin gach gip gok, suŋ-tep mindonjun aŋgiy, ñin maŋgiy ñiŋg ayokiy mindenimimb. Pen nimb Gor nup kisen gipun aŋgiy yesek apim gok, gos omiŋal ma niŋiy, Gor nup nep chiŋgnimimb.  
\v 9 Sik apim ak kirgiy, simb gakniŋ siy aŋgyiŋg mindenimimb.  
\v 10 Biyomb niŋmindip rek, biynimb tep ma mindpim ak niŋiy aŋgem mey; nimbip direp giniŋgamb.   
\p
\v 11 Mam ay sikop. Mam ay gunap kuyip yenen kun gipay aŋgiy, kuyip aŋgsikoy ma ginimimb. Biynimb mam ay aŋgsikoy gipay gok, Gor low nuk ak yenen mer aŋgip aŋgiy, sesek aŋg sikoy gipay. Kun ak biynimb Gor low kisen gipay rek ma mindeniŋgambim; low nuk tep mindip akaŋ, yerip rek mindip aŋgiy, gos piyow niŋbay rek ak mindeniŋgambim.  
\v 12 Gor nep low ayak; nuk nep biynimb deprek ayip gok diy, biynimb ma deprek ayip gok kirgip. Kun ak nimb Biyomb mindip rek mindiy mey; “Biynimb gok mindrep gipay; biynimb gok mindrep ma gipay aŋgiy,” apim ak?   
\s1 Yimb Nimb Ma Dand Aranimimb  
\p
\v 13 Pen niŋim. Nimb gunap apim, miñiy akaŋ toy rek, miñmon yomb bap amiy, kun okok simiy nokom bap woŋg biysniys giy, maniy yomb diniŋgambun apim. Pen niŋrep ginimimb.  
\v 14 Gor kisen yerer giniŋgamb ak niŋiy ma apim. Miñiy kim mindpun ak pen; kim mindpun kun ak, yuk biñ ak gip rek nep gip. Won ak mindip, won ak kapkap kurgek amimb.  
\v 15 Gip kun ak rek, minim apim kun ak kirgiy aŋgnimimb, “Gor nup tep geniŋgamb, chinup kond mindakniŋ kim mindiy, woŋg kun kun giniŋgambun aŋgnimimb.”  
\v 16 Pen biyomb biynyomb mindpun aŋgiy, yimb key dand aranbun ak tep ma gip.   
\p
\v 17 Miñ tep ar ginimimb aŋgip ak niŋiy, pen ma giniŋgambun ak; Gor niŋek tap siy tap timey giniŋgambun.   
\c 5  
\s1 Biynimb Tap Kuŋay Mindip Gok  
\p
\v 1 Nimb biynimb gin yimb gok, minim aŋgniŋg gispiyn ak niŋim! Miker yomb diniŋg gispim rek, simb gek siy aŋgnimimb.  
\v 2 Chech tap nimb kuŋay mindip gok, siplep siwiy kuyiŋg yasaw.  
\v 3 Gol, maniy, siylpa nimb gok simbsis gisap rek, tap siy tap timey gipim ak niŋrep ginimimb. Ñin kisen ak maŋ asaw rek, tap nan-gispim gok, mumbwak nimbik ak, mon yinsimbok amemb rek ak gispim.  
\v 4 Biynimb woŋg nimbip gipay gok, kuyip pey ñirep ma gem, kosyam mindpay ak, siy aŋgey, Biyomb kalrimey semb biyoŋ mindip ak niŋimb.  
\v 5 Per man ar biy mindiy, woŋg wariy ma giy, yikop mindiy miñmiñ yimb girapim. Kun ak kanj gok mokrep giy, guk gek pikñimbay rek mindpim ak, won par ma mindeniŋgambim.  
\v 6 Biynimb tep, nimbip tap bap ma gipay gok kuyip, yesek aŋgiy ñapim.   
\s1 Miker Apek Yiruk Ma Niŋiy, Gor Nup Kond Mindonjun  
\p
\v 7 Kun ak mam ay sikop. Yiruk ma niŋjun; Biyomb chin asaw aŋgiy kond mindonjun. Biynimb tap woŋg gi yimiy, kond mindyakniŋ pumb niŋiy, miñmon pikiy, jakek nep ñimbay rek, nup kond mindonjun.  
\v 8 Biyomb ñin nuk winiŋgamb ak yep maŋ mindip aŋgiy, gos sek kond mindonjun.   
\p
\v 9 Pen mam ay sikop. Gor niŋmindip rek, mam ay gunap kuyip ma aŋgjiwnimimb. Bi kor niŋniŋgamb ak maŋ asaw.  
\v 10 Bi Gor minim aŋgep wosrey mindyiŋgipay gok kuyip timey giyakniŋ, kosyam yimb mindyiŋgipay ak pen; kapkap mindrep giyak. Ar kun ak nep ginimimb.  
\v 11 Nimb niŋbim: biynimb kun gok rek, mindrep gipay apun. Kun ak binak Job wosrey mindyiŋgip kesim ak, sakiy ma ginimimb. Nup miker yomb apek, kosyam mindek ñin ak, Gor nup gosimb niŋyiŋg kapkap mindiy, mind dand amnakniŋ, Gor gi tep gek, mindrep yimb gak. Yenen: nuk biynimb simb niŋiy, direp yimb gip.   
\p
\v 12 Pen mam ay sikop. Tap yomb yimb ak, Gor nup yimb ak yikop ma aŋgnimimb. Bi semb biyoŋ sek, lum biy sek gayak ak niŋmindip rek, niŋind aspiyn aŋgiy, ma aŋgnimimb. Yaw aŋgiy, yaw nep aŋgnimimb. Mer aŋgiy, mer nep aŋgnimimb. Yikop ak minim yomb yimb diniŋgambim.   
\p
\v 13 Pen tep gek miñmiñ gun aŋgiy, Gor nup kamep aŋgnimimb; miker gonimuŋ nup aŋgniŋnimimb.  
\v 14 Biynimb nimbip gunap tap gonimuŋ, biyomb Gor biynimb nuk kond mindpay gok aŋgem apiy, Biyomb chin ak gek suŋ ayniŋgamb aŋgiy, nup aŋgniŋiy, wel di jun kuyip biyoŋ ayñiniŋgiy.  
\v 15 Pen Gor nup gosimb niŋiy aŋgniŋeniŋgambay, nuk gek tap giniŋgamb kun ak, suŋ ayniŋgamb. Tap siy tap timey giyak gok, kunep niŋiy kirginiŋgamb.   
\p
\v 16 Kun ak nen, tap siy tap timey gipim gok, penpen aŋgyiknimimb. Aŋgyikiy, Gor nup aŋgniŋem, nuk gek suŋ mindeniŋgambim. Biynimb suŋ-tep gok nup aŋgniŋey, nuk key yimb giniŋgamb.  
\v 17 Bi Gor minim aŋgep Yilayja, bi yikop chin rek ak pen, Gor nup aŋgniŋek, simiy omiŋal nokom, takin anep kaŋgol ak, miñmon ma pikak.  
\v 18 Kisen pen tip ak Gor nup aŋgniŋek, miñmon pikiy tap woŋg gok jakak.   
\p
\v 19-20 Mam ay sikop. Biynimb nimb gunap, minim yipul yimb ak kirgey, kuyip aŋgñirep gem, tip ak Gor nup gosimb niŋniŋgambay ak; tep yimb giniŋgambim. Kun giy mey, tap siy tap timey yerip yerip giyak gok niŋiy kirgek mey, kumiy pisnep ma kumniŋgambay.   